英文文本: Error:   Connection failed! Please check your network, then try again.

中文文本:
尊敬的用户，狩猎大陆发生了一些变化，需要更新{0}的更新包。
继续下载可能产生流量费用，是否继续下载？
英文文本: Dear user, some changes have happened in the world of Hunterold. You need to download the updates of {0}.\n If you download now, it may cause data fees. Continue?

中文文本: 网络状态变更，继续下载可能产生流量费用，是否继续下载？
英文文本: Your network status has just changed. If you continue to download now, it may cause data fees. Continue?

中文文本:
是否清理本地缓存的游戏资源以及账号信息？
当游戏运行有问题时，也可通过此操作解决部分异常问题。
需要重新下载补丁包及游戏扩展资源。
英文文本: Are you sure you wish to delete the local cached game data and account info?\n If the game could not run normally in your device, you can do so to fix some problems.\n But you will have to redownload the latest updates and the corresponding expansion sets.

英文文本: Dear user, some changes have happened in the world of Hunterold. Please update it in the App Store.

中文文本: 清除缓存中，此过程不消耗流量……
英文文本: Deleting cached data without cost of date fees...
